  <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
  <p>Thank you for shopping with Coffee Shop. If you are not entirely satisfied with your purchase, we're here to help.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Returns</h2>
  <p>We do not accept returns for perishable goods such as coffee and food items. Please contact us immediately if there
    is an issue with your order.</p>

  <h2>2. Refunds</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>If you receive a damaged or incorrect item, you may be eligible for a full refund.</li>
    <li>Refund requests must be made within 2 days of delivery.</li>
    <li>Provide your order number and a clear photo of the item when requesting a refund.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Cancellations</h2>
  <p>You may cancel your order within 15 minutes of placing it. After that time, the order may already be in preparation
    and cannot be canceled.</p>

  <h2>4. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about our refund policy, please contact us at:</p>
  <p>Email: info@coffeeshopwebsite.com</p>
  <p>Phone: (+91) 7437867006</p>

